# IDE-Like UX Overhaul — Walkthrough

VibeMarketer has been transformed from a simple sidebar+form app into an **IDE-like workspace** — designed to feel powerful but never intimidating for non-technical users.

## What Changed

### New Components
| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| **Activity Bar** | Narrow icon column (Home, Skills, Settings) with API status dot |
| **Tab Bar** | Multi-tab skill switching — open, close, and switch between skills |
| **Status Bar** | Bottom bar: "15 skills available · API connected · Ready" |
| **Home Dashboard** | Quick-start cards, setup prompt, full skill directory |

### Modified Components
| Component | Changes |
|-----------|---------|
| **App.jsx** | Complete rewrite — tab state, collapsible sidebar, per-skill output tracking |
| **Sidebar.jsx** | Search filter added, settings/titlebar removed (moved to Activity Bar) |
| **index.css** | Full CSS rewrite — grid layout for IDE shell, all new component styles |

